d="bc7a3320-ea62-4c62-930e-56377dd27869" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>Gender Equality & Empowerment</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="bc7a3320-ea62-4c62-930e-56377dd27869" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-bBHHxi ezvCRe pf-68_"><div class="sc-clIzBv iQyrr pf-69_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-gnnDb bRALxe pf-70_"><p class="sc-DtmNo VpbqT pf-71_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fivaXQ OAMge pf-73_">At AYA, we accept workers of all genders. Our company consists of our founders, marketing team, art team, assistants, accountants and production workers. As of May 2022, we have 36 employees and freelancers working with us, 27 of whom are women.</span></p><p class="sc-DtmNo VpbqT pf-74_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fivaXQ OAMge pf-76_">Everyone at AYA can use their voice freely to disclose their opinions and ideas. They have a high level of autonomy in their day-to-day activities.&nbsp;</span></p></div></div></div></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-AjmGg eCTxfx pf-77_"><button type="button" class="sc-dPiLbb jUujTN pf-78_ pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="7dd27869-2fb9-479c-bc8d-444cbe51ea65" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>Racial Justice</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="7dd27869-2fb9-479c-bc8d-444cbe51ea65" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-bBHHxi ezvCRe pf-80_"><div class="sc-clIzBv iQyrr pf-81_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-gnnDb bRALxe pf-82_"><p class="sc-DtmNo VpbqT pf-83_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fivaXQ OAMge pf-85_">AYA is an inclusive brand which is why nobody is discriminated for their nationality or color. Our team is formed of people of different ethnicities, who contribute to the company's development with their unique knowledge and perspective. Our employees and freelancers are from the United States, Latin America and Europe.</span></p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:6"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-gnnDb bRALxe pf-86_"><div data-pf-type="Image" class="sc-ewSTlh klfUNH pf-87_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0550/2880/9974/t/8/assets/workerstudio-1657038956874_1200x.jpg?v=1657038958" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0550/2880/9974/t/8/assets/workerstudio-1657038956874.jpg?v=1657038958 1536w" width="1080" height="1080" sizes="(min-width: 1536px) 1536px, (min-width: 1024px) 1280px, (min-width: 640px) 768px, 320px" loading="lazy"/></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-section-id="pf-9fb8" data-pf-type="Section" class="sc-itWPBs CnKWk pf-88_ pf-bg-lazy"><div style="--cw:1170px" class="sc-gHjyzD dqPPVt"><div class="sc-clIzBv iQyrr pf-89_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c pf-hide" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:6"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-gnnDb bRALxe pf-90_ pf-bg-lazy pf-hide"></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:6"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-gnnDb bRALxe pf-91_"><h2 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-jlsrNB jrZWiU pf-92_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fivaXQ OAMge pf-94_">Our Goals</span></h2><p class="sc-DtmNo VpbqT pf-95_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fivaXQ OAMge pf-97_">We made sure that from the start everything on our end is done legally and without causing any harm. But that is not where it ends for us. We aim to:</span></p><ul style="--text-indent:0;--line-spaci